  "detailed_description": "<h1>💟CHECK THIS OUT!💟</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>This game is SFW version of Last Devil. For updates, please visit the MangoCouncil official website.</strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/2ca383591f9451760e2581b8060fa606.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=402 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/082e4e6961e5d60fe468c1a5c1e379de.webp?t=1700754722\" width=615 height=40 /></span><br><br>Survive the wilderness, gather companions, and restore your throne to its former glory in this fast-paced roguelite shooting game! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/2bed2d878fb9de723bb31704762e0016.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/2bed2d878fb9de723bb31704762e0016.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/2bed2d878fb9de723bb31704762e0016.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/fd72295de59bd4e19301d1593e4b7abf.webp?t=1700754722\" width=615 height=40 /></span><br><strong><br>【WASD】 Movement<br>【F】 Interact/Open<br>【LMB】 Normal Attack<br>【RMB】 Skill<br>【Space】 Dash<br>【Q】 Throw<br>【E】 Companion Skill<br>【P】 Suicide<br>【TAB】 Backpack<br>【ESC】 Options</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/41fbf1b4280a7b63f34523df8cc74af8.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/a0f229ae4e4fbe237a5e1dea506cdc37.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/b36ed5070fbe4b633f1b4f03e080fd2d.webp?t=1700754722\" width=615 height=40 /></span><br><br><strong>1. Collect items and stack buffs to upgrade your skills and abilities. 【Create your own builds】</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/c6bd5ed43e25b8748c0e46a7116102ae.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/c6bd5ed43e25b8748c0e46a7116102ae.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/c6bd5ed43e25b8748c0e46a7116102ae.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/d2751ead3298a60992144a55b1b0f12b.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/d2751ead3298a60992144a55b1b0f12b.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/d2751ead3298a60992144a55b1b0f12b.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2. Smooth and intuitive combat. Use Dash to dodge attacks and execute your counterattack!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/8e9cbd931099a93972734c78f7adca04.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/8e9cbd931099a93972734c78f7adca04.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/8e9cbd931099a93972734c78f7adca04.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3. Anything can happen on an adventure! Interact with characters, events environments to pick up new abilities... or crippling curses.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/9c47c05bf31ad0fd394ef9cc8bb74e78.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/9c47c05bf31ad0fd394ef9cc8bb74e78.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/9c47c05bf31ad0fd394ef9cc8bb74e78.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4. Get all lovey-dovey with the three main characters as you experience their stories. Find out their needs, and let them satisfy yours...</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/91a1b99d899adf77c028cfdb057f9c4f.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/91a1b99d899adf77c028cfdb057f9c4f.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/91a1b99d899adf77c028cfdb057f9c4f.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>5. Completing the campaign unlocks and infinite challenge mode, with more random events and stronger enemies.【For gamers who relish a challenge】</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/8f3928cf75a98f7dacb0aed2df701c16.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/8f3928cf75a98f7dacb0aed2df701c16.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/8f3928cf75a98f7dacb0aed2df701c16.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>6. Take cover using the rich and varied environments, but watch out! Some of them can be destroyed...</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/05b1aa29599cca68c7010c2400ca7802.poster.avif?t=1700754722\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/05b1aa29599cca68c7010c2400ca7802.webm?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014740/extras/05b1aa29599cca68c7010c2400ca7802.mp4?t=1700754722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
